{"tid":1050603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HK No IT 警搜鴨寮街影碟店　再檢鹹碟拉人 （19年3月）","createTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T04:04:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"264a313d7b71f2dd4f9eb2a72714a9ab2fa7fd2e","tid":1050603,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:51:52.000Z","msg":"深水埗警區特別職務隊根據線報調查後，今日（6日）下午5時許，展開一項反淫褻物品行動，突擊搜查鴨寮街141號一間影碟店，檢獲約5000隻色情光碟，總值約14萬港元，當場拘捕一名姓周（61歲）男子，以涉嫌「發布淫褻物品」及「管有淫褻物品以供發布用途」扣留調查。據了解，涉案影碟店的舖位，以往曾多次被警方破獲出售色情光碟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/bkn-20190306235525477-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fbkn-20190306235525477-0306_00822_001.html&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=80257e2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/bkn-20190306235525477-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f65ce18cae52bb369c1db237bac1237f43180fd","tid":1050603,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306235525477-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190306235535\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306235525477-0306_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190306235535&h=32b23370&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a62fb5858eab6ce2c8e5da4614494f1ba5e53cc7","tid":1050603,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"冇高清，不了"},{"pid":"fd4160ae429ef4cdf5a0f1dcd3c7c0193e9a9f75","tid":1050603,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"2019仲賣咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ced33937c9e14047411fa24c16551eda7d962b","tid":1050603,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quo